70.8	Donna_Haraway	Donna Haraway	Donna J. Haraway (born September 6, 1944 in Denver, Colorado) is currently a Distinguished Professor Emerita in the History of Consciousness Department at the University of California, Santa Cruz, United States. Haraway has been described as a "feminist, rather loosely a neo-Marxist and a postmodernist" (Young, 172).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/41/Donna_Haraway_and_Cayenne.jpg/270px-Donna_Haraway_and_Cayenne.jpg
